Package edu.uky.cs.nil.sabre.bench

Interface Statistic<N extends Number>

Type Parameters:
N - the type of number output by the statistic's calculation
public interface Statistic<N extends Number>
A statistic is a calculation to be performed on a collection of numeric values. Statistics that operate on integers all use long values, and statistics that operator on decimal numbers all use double values.
